[root@controller ~(keystonerc_demo)]$ neutron help router-create
usage: neutron router-create [-h] [-f {json,shell,table,value,yaml}]
                             [-c COLUMN] [--max-width <integer>] [--noindent]
                             [--prefix PREFIX] [--request-format {json,xml}]
                             [--tenant-id TENANT_ID] [--admin-state-down]
                             NAME

Create a router for a given tenant.

positional arguments:
  NAME                  Name of router to create
  distributed           Create a distributed router ("""" VMware NSX plugin only """")




